s390: vfio-ap: implement VFIO_DEVICE_GET_INFO ioctl

Adds support for the VFIO_DEVICE_GET_INFO ioctl to the VFIO
AP Matrix device driver. This is a minimal implementation,
as vfio-ap does not use I/O regions.

